BABYSITTER KATA NIGHTLY CHARGE APP

This app has a couple components
- backend flask app(/backend)
- frontend React JS app (/frontend)
- tests /backend/tests

Start the backend:
- start the venv (venv/Scripts/activate)
- cd into /backend
- pip install -r requirements.txt
- python app.py

Start the frontend
- cd frontend
- npm install
- npm start

Run the tests
- python -m pytest

Future Additions:
- Only allow the user to select times in range and make end/bed time dynamic to the start time. User shouldn't be able to select and end time before the start time in the select menu (frontend)

- Expand testing to frontend

- Expand testing to flask app not just business logic

